(11, 1, '2018-02-22 11:35:30', '2018-02-22 11:35:30', '<h2>What We Do Best</h2>		\n		<p>If you want to learn more about us, you\'re in the right place. Read to learn how we managed to grow our business so fast.</p>		\n                <h3>\n                    Facebook\n                </h3>\n                <p>https://www.facebook.com/subhashyadav275</p>\n                <h3>\n                    Twitter\n                </h3>\n                <p>https://twitter.com/kumrsubhash?lang=en</p>\n                <h3>\n                    Youtube\n                </h3>\n                <p>https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKgUk_SL2vkLV-lthgJAUpw</p>\n			<h3>We are just good with dealing tehnology\n</h3>		\n			<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/algorithm.jpg" alt="algorithm" title="algorithm"></figure><h3>Algorithems</h3><p>In mathematics and computer science, an algorithm is an unambiguous specification of how to solve a class of problems. Algorithms can perform calculation, data processing and automated reasoning tasks</p>		\n			<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/machine-learning-ml_logo.png" alt="machine-learning-ml_logo" title="machine-learning-ml_logo"></figure><h3>Machine learning</h3><p>Machine learning is a field of computer science that gives computer systems the ability to "learn" with data, without being explicitly programmed. The name Machine learning was coined in 1959 by Arthur Samuel.</p>		\n			<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/code.png" alt="code" title="code"></figure><h3>Programming</h3><p>Computer programming is a process that leads from an original formulation of a computing problem to executable computer programs.</p>		\n			<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Data-Science-vs.-Big-Data-vs.jpg" alt="Data-Science-vs.-Big-Data-vs" title="Data-Science-vs.-Big-Data-vs"></figure><h3>Data Analysis</h3><p>Data analysis, also known as analysis of data or data analytics, is a process of inspecting, cleansing, transforming, and modeling data with the goal of discovering useful information, suggesting conclusions, and supporting decision-making.</p>		\n			<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Tensorflow_logo.svg.png" alt="Tensorflow_logo.svg" title="Tensorflow_logo.svg"></figure><h3>Tensor Flow</h3><p>TensorFlow is an open-source software library for dataflow programming across a range of tasks. It is a symbolic math library, and also used for machine learning applications such as neural networks.</p>		\n			<figure><img src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/AI.png" alt="AI" title="AI"></figure><h3>AI</h3><p>Artificial intelligence is intelligence demonstrated by machines, in contrast to the natural intelligence displayed by humans and other animals.​</p>		\n			<h1>We can help you with...</h1>		\n				Design\n									80%\n				Machine Learning\n									75%\n				Wordpress\n									100%\n				Python\n									86%\n			<h3>Lets Code From Now.</h3>		\n			<a href="http://localhost/wordpress/index.php/contact/">\n						Start\n					</a>', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2018-02-22 18:13:51', '2018-02-22 18:13:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
