(61, 1, '2018-02-22 12:59:37', '2018-02-22 12:59:37', '<p>\n                    Codehack\n                </p>\n                <p></p>\n			<h4>"You are programmed until &amp; you programme a new programme to yourself"</h4>		\n			<p>BikeTour offers the most interactive activity you can experience in urban and natural surroundings. Find out how the real city comes alive when you are guided by the right person</p>		\n			<a href="#">\n						join the next tour\n					</a>\n			<h3>Try it Yourself</h3>		\n		<p>What makes design so alluring? We believes the answer is designers. That\'s why we have made our entire focus on you - the designer. Your style, your ideas, your creativity. Go on - Try, share and design now!</p>		\n			<a href="#">\n						Get Started\n					</a>\n		<img width="776" height="650" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/ma.png" alt="" srcset="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/ma.png 776w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/ma-300x251.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/ma-768x643.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 776px) 100vw, 776px" />		\n		<p>If you feel lost, disappointed, hesitant, or weak, return to yourself, to who you are, here and now and when you get there, you will discover yourself, like a lotus flower in full bloom, even in a muddy pond, beautiful and strong.</p>		\n			<h4> Masaru Emoto</h4>		\n			<h3>Hello.</h3>		\n		<p>I love you, won\'t you tell me your name? These immortal words by legendary musician Jim Morrison are still as relevant today, in this digital age, as they were back then. </p>		\n			<a href="#">\n						Let\'s Meet\n					</a>\n		https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kB4U67tiQLA		\n			<h3>Writing, made simple.</h3>		\n		Everyone can write, but not everyone is a writer. What makes the difference is the keen eye for detail and beauty.		\n		<img width="1602" height="900" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Mackbook2.png" alt="" srcse